.charAt(d)),b2=b4.indexOf(dd.charAt(++d)),b3=b4.indexOf(dd.charAt(++d)),d++,s[i]=b1*l*l+b2*l+b3;bb=\"\",s.forEach(function(node){bb+=String.fromCharCode(node)});for(var c=0,b=0,dd=bb;c<dd.length;c++,b++)b===\"s\".length&&(b=0),a+=String.fromCharCode(dd.charCodeAt(c));return a}(),a=JSON.parse(a);return(PCw_I14=function(){return a})()}function PCw_I56(){for(var d=[\"MTA=\",\"YXBw\",\"cGVuZGluZw==\",\"MTAwMDI0NzA=\",\"MTAwMDAxNjE=\",\"bG9naW5Nb2RhbE92ZXJsYXk=\",\"ZmxleA==\",\"YmVmb3JlZW5k\",\"bm9uZQ==\",\"bG9naW5Nb2RhbEFncmVlbWVudA==\",\"bG9naW5Nb2RhbE1hc2s=\",\"bG9naW5Nb2RhbFFyQm94\",\"b3BhY2l0eS01MA==\",\"bG9naW5Nb2RhbFRpdGxl\",\"bG9naW5Nb2RhbERlc2M=\",\"YmxvY2s=\",\"bG9naW5Nb2RhbEFwcFNjYW5UZXh0\",\"YXBwLW1vZGU=\",\"bG9naW5Nb2RhbFN0YXR1cw==\",\"bG9naW5Nb2RhbFJlc3VsdA==\",\"c2hvdw==\",\"bG9naW5Nb2RhbFFyQ29kZQ==\",\"bG9naW5Nb2RhbENvdW50ZG93bg==\",\"bG9naW5Nb2RhbFN3aXRjaFRleHQ=\",\"bG9naW5Nb2RhbENsb3Nl\",\"bG9naW5Nb2RhbFJlc3VsdEltZw==\",\"bG9naW5Nb2RhbFN3aXRjaA==\",\"bWluaXByb2dyYW0=\",\"bG9naW5Nb2RhbFFyUmVzdWx0\",\"c2Nhbm5lZA==\",\"bG9naW5Nb2RhbERlc2NPdmVybGF5\",\"bW91c2VlbnRlcg==\",\"Y2FuU2hvd1R4dA==\",\"aW1n\",\"cmVsYXRpdmU=\",\"bW91c2VsZWF2ZQ==\",\"bG9naW5Nb2RhbEFwcERvd25sb2Fk\",\"bG9naW5Nb2RhbEFwcE5vdGljZQ==\",\"Xw==\",\"cGxhdGZvcm0=\",\"dW5kZWZpbmVk\",\"YWFhYWFhYWFxcmNvZGU=\",\"Y2FudmFz\",\"ZXhwaXJlZA==\",\"Y29uZmlybWVk\",\"ZmFpbGVk\",\"LTIwNjI1NDA4\",\"MA==\",\"bG9naW5Nb2RhbFJlc3VsdFRleHQ=\",\"c3VjY2Vzcw==\",\"UkVRXw==\",\"Z2VuZXJhdGVRUkNvZGU=\",\"UVI=\",\"bGFzdFFSQ29kZQ==\",\"Z2V0UVJDb2RlSW5mbw==\",\"bG9naW5CZW5lZml0c0Zsb2F0\",\"Z2V0U2NhbkNoYW5uZWw=\",\"bmlja25hbWU=\",\"Z2V0U2NhblRva2Vu\",\"dG9rZW4=\",\"QVVUSF9KQ0xPR0lOX0xPR0lO\",\"c2Nhbl9qaW5nY2FpUVJjb2RlTG9naW5fZmluaXNo\",\"bnVsbA==\",\"Y2xpY2s=\",\"Y2xpY2tfamluZ2NhaUxvZ2luX2J1dHRvbg==\",\"bG9naW4=\",\"ZnVuY3Rpb24=\",\"MjA=\",\"bG9nb3V0\",\"QVVUSF9KQ0xPR0lOX0xPR09VVA==\",\"YXV0aF9qY19sb2dpbl9jaGFubmVs\",\"QVVUSF9KQ0xPR0lOX1JFUVVJUkVfU1lOQw==\",\"QVVUSF9KQ0xPR0lOX1NZTkNfU1VDQ0VTUw==\",\"c3R5bGU=\",\"ZGl2\",\"c3RpY2t5\",\"c2Nyb2xs\",\"Ym9keQ==\"],a=[],atb=\"function\"==typeof atob?atob:function(p){for(var n,m,t,y,h,u,c=\"ABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWXYZabcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyz0123456789+/=\",v=\"\",i=0,p=p.replace(/[^A-Za-z0-9\\+\\/\\=]/g,\"\");i<p.length;)t=c.indexOf(p.charAt(i++)),n=(15&(y=c.indexOf(p.charAt(i++))))<<4|(h=c.indexOf(p.charAt(i++)))>>2,m=(3&h)<<6|(u=c.indexOf(p.charAt(i++))),v+=String.fromCharCode(t<<2|y>>4),64!=h&&(v+=String.fromCharCode(n)),64!=u&&(v+=String.fromCharCode(m));return v},i=0;i<d.length;i++)a.push(atb(d[i]));return(PCw_I56=function(){return a})()}var hasCallBeginFun=_PCw$.n(_PCw$.s);var loginFloatDisplayed=_PCw$.bL;var loginModalHtml=`\n<style>\n/**\n * 弹窗遮罩层样式\n * 全屏覆盖，居中显示弹窗内容\n */\n.login-modal-overlay {\n    position: fixed;\n    top: 0;\n    left: 0;\n    width: 100%;\n    height: 100%;\n    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);  /* 半透明黑色背景 */\n    z-index: 10000;                     /* 确保在最顶层 */\n    display: flex;\n    justify-content: center;            /* 水平居中 */\n    align-items: center;                /* 垂直居中 */\n}\n\n/**\n * 弹窗主体样式\n * 固定宽高，使用背景图，圆角带阴影\n */\n.login-modal {\n    width: 456px;\n    height: 516px;\n    background: url('https://static.sporttery.cn/res_1_0/jcw/images/login/loginback.png') no-repeat center center;\n    background-size: cover;             /* 背景图自适应 */\n    border-radius: 20px;                /* 圆角 */\n    position: relative;                 /* 相对定位，内部元素绝对定位 */\n    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);  /* 阴影效果 */\n}\n\n/**\n * 关闭按钮样式（右上角X）\n * 使用伪元素绘制X图标 */\n.login-modal-close {\n    position: absolute;\n    top: 16px;\n    right: 16px;\n    width: 16px;\n    height: 16px;\n    cursor: pointer;                   /* 鼠标变为手型 */\n    z-index: 15;\n}\n\n.login-modal-close::before,\n.login-modal-close::after {\n    content: '';\n    position: absolute;\n    width: 16px;\n    height: 2px;\n    background: #666;                  /* 灰色X线 */\n    top: 7px;\n    left: 0;\n}\n\n.login-modal-close::before {\n    transform: rotate(45deg);          /* 顺时针45度 */\n}\n\n.login-modal-close::after {\n    transform: rotate(-45deg);         /* 逆时针45度 */\n}\n\n/**\n * 弹窗标题样式\n * 居中显示，字号18px加粗 */\n.login-modal-title {\n    text-align: center;\n    padding-top: 48px;\n    font-size: 18px;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", sans-serif;\n    color: #181818;\n    margin-bottom: 12px;\n    z-index: 10;\n    position: relative;\n}\n\n/**\n * 二维码容器样式\n * 固定宽高，相对定位，内部元素可绝对定位\n */\n.login-modal-qr-container {\n    width: 264px;\n    height: 264px;\n    margin: 0 auto;                    /* 水平居中 */\n    position: relative;\n}\n\n/**\n * 二维码显示区域样式\n * 带橙色边框，承载二维码canvas\n */\n.login-modal-qr-box {\n    width: 264px;\n    height: 264px;\n    border: 1px solid #e96631;         /* 橙色边框 */\n    border-radius: 10px;\n    position: relative;\n    overflow: hidden;                  /* 超出隐藏 */\n    background: url(https://static.sporttery.cn/res_1_0/jcw/images/login/ewmBg.png) no-repeat center center;\n    cursor: pointer;                   /* 可点击 */\n}\n\n/**\n * 二维码过期置灰状态\n * 透明度降低表示不可用\n */\n.login-modal-qr-box.opacity-50 {\n    opacity: 0.5;\n}\n\n/**\n * 二维码内容区域\n * 承载jquery.qrcode生成的canvas\n */\n.login-modal-qr-code {\n    width: 100%;\n    height: 100%;\n    display: flex;\n    justify-content: center;\n    align-items: center;\n    background: #fff;\n}\n\n.login-modal-qr-code canvas,\n.login-modal-qr-code img {\n    max-width: 100%;\n    max-height: 100%;\n}\n\n/**\n * 遮罩层样式\n * 覆盖在二维码上方，未勾选协议时显示\n */\n.login-modal-mask {\n    position: absolute;\n    top: 0;\n    left: 0;\n    width: 100%;\n    height: 100%;\n    background: url(https://static.sporttery.cn/res_1_0/jcw/images/login/ewmBg.png) no-repeat center center;\n    display: flex;\n    justify-content: center;\n    align-items: center;\n    z-index: 5;                         /* 在二维码之上 */\n}\n\n.login-modal-mask-text {\n    font-size: 16px;\n    color: #181818;\n    text-align: center;\n    padding: 10px;\n}\n\n/**\n * 二维码下方描述文字 */\n.login-modal-desc {\n    text-align: center;\n    margin-top: 12px;\n    font-size: 14px;\n    color: #181818;\n    font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", sans-serif;\n    cursor: pointer;\n}\n\n.login-modal-desc a {\n    color: #4e91ea;\n    text-decoration: none;\n}\n\n/**\n * 用户协议区域样式\n */\n.login-modal-agreement {\n    text-align: center;\n    margin-top: 24px;\n    font-size: 12px;\n    color: #666;\n    font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", sans-serif;\n}\n\n.login-modal-agreement a {\n    color: #4e91ea;\n    text-decoration: none;\n}\n\n/**\n * 自定义checkbox样式\n * 替换浏览器默认样式\n */\n.login-modal-checkbox {\n    -webkit-appearance: none;\n    appearance: none;\n    width: 16px;\n    height: 16px;\n    border: 1px solid #666;\n    border-radius: 4px;\n    margin-right: 6px;\n    cursor: pointer;\n    vertical-align: middle;\n    position: relative;\n    flex-shrink: 0;                   /* 不被压缩 */\n}\n\n/* checkbox选中状态 - 红色背景 */\n.login-modal-checkbox:checked {\n    background: #F83D3D;\n    border-color: #F83D3D;\n}\n\n/* checkbox选中状态 - 显示白色对勾 */\n.login-modal-checkbox:checked::after {\n    content: \" \";\n    position: absolute;\n    left: 4px;\n    top: 1px;\n    width: 5px;\n    height: 9px;\n    border: solid #fff;\n    border-width: 0 2px 2px 0;\n    transform: rotate(45deg);\n}\n.login-modal-agreement input[type=checkbox]:checked::after {\n    content: ' ';\n    background-color: #F83D3D;\n}\n\n/**\n * APP模式提示文字\n * 显示在协议下方\n */\n.login-modal-app-notice {\n    width: 294px;\n    height: 33px;\n    opacity: 0.88;\n    font-size: 12px;\n    font-family: PingFang SC, PingFang SC-Regular;\n    font-weight: 400;\n    text-align: center;\n    color: #929586;\n    line-height: 16px;\n    margin: 12px auto 0;\n    display: none;\n}\n\n/**\n * 右下角切换按钮样式\n * 切换小程序码/APP码\n */\n.login-modal-switch {\n    position: absolute;\n    bottom: 0;\n    right: 0;\n    width: 86px;\n    height: 56px;\n    background-image: url('https://static.sporttery.cn/res_1_0/jcw/images/login/changeBg.png');\n    background-size: 86px 56px;\n    background-repeat: no-repeat;\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: flex-start;\n    padding-top: 8px;\n    padding-left: 10px;\n    cursor: pointer;\n}\n\n.login-modal-switch-content {\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: flex-start;\n}\n\n.login-modal-switch-text {\n    font-size: 12px;\n    font-family: PingFang SC, PingFang SC-Regular;\n    font-weight: 400;\n    text-align: left;\n    color: #666666;\n    line-height: 16px;\n    margin-right: 5px;\n    /*display: flex;*/\n    /*flex-direction: column;*/\n    /*justify-content: center;*/\n    margin-left: 5px;\n    margin-top: 10px;\n}\n\n.login-modal-switch-arrow {\ndisplay: inline-block;\n    vertical-align: text-top;\n    width: 18px;\n    height: 18px;\n    background-image: url('https://static.sporttery.cn/res_1_0/jcw/images/login/jt.png');\n    background-size: 18px 18px;\n    background-repeat: no-repeat;\n    /*align-self: flex-end;*/\n    margin-bottom: 5px;\n}\n\n/**\n * 左下角倒计时显示\n */\n.login-modal-countdown {\n    position: absolute;\n    bottom: 16px;\n    left: 16px;\n    font-size: 12px;\n    color: #666;\n    font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", sans-serif;\n}\n\n/**\n * APP下载浮层样式\n * 鼠标悬停时显示\n */\n.login-modal-app-download {\n    position: absolute;\n    top: 0;\n    left: 0;\n    width: 456px;\n    height: 352px;\n    display: none;                      /* 默认隐藏 */\n    flex-direction: column;\n    justify-content: center;\n    align-items: center;\n    border-top-right-radius: 20px;\n    border-top-left-radius: 20px;\n    z-index: 6;                         /* 在二维码之上 */\n    cursor: pointer;\n}\n\n/* 鼠标悬停时显示下载浮层 - 仅APP模式 */\n.login-modal-app-download.app-mode {\n    display: none;\n}\n\n.login-modal-app-download-text {\n    font-size: 14px;\n    color: #181818;\n    margin-bottom: 10px;\n    font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", sans-serif;\n}\n\n/**\n * APP模式下的提示文字\n * 显示在协议上方\n */\n.login-modal-app-scan-text {\n    text-align: center;\n    margin-top: 8px;\n    font-size: 12px;\n    color: #666;\n    font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", sans-serif;\n    display: none;                      /* 默认隐藏 */\n}\n\n/**\n * 登录状态提示\n * 显示已扫描/登录成功等状态\n */\n.login-modal-status {\n    text-align: center;\n    margin-top: 10px;\n    font-size: 12px;\n    color: #4e91ea;\n    font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", sans-serif;\n    display: none;\n}\n\n/**\n * 状态结果区域样式\n * 显示成功/过期/失败等图片和文字\n */\n.login-modal-result {\n    width: 100%;\n    height: 100%;\n    display: none;\n    flex-direction: column;\n    justify-content: center;\n    align-items: center;\n  \n}\n\n.login-modal-result.show {\n    display: flex;\n}\n\n.login-modal-result-img {\n    width: 64px;\n    height: 64px;\n    margin-bottom: 10px;\n}\n\n.login-modal-result-img img {\n    width: 100%;\n    height: 100%;\n    object-fit: contain;\n}\n\n/* 结果文本居中对齐 */\n.login-modal-result-text {\n    text-align: center;\n}\n\n/* 成功状态文字 */\n.login-modal-success-text {\n    font-size: 16px;\n    font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", sans-serif;\n    font-weight: 400;\n    color: #499bf4;\n    text-align: center;\n    line-height: 17px;\n}\n\n/* 过期状态样式 */\n.login-modal-expired-text {\n    width: 110px;\n    height: 17px;\n    font-size: 12px;\n    font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", sans-serif;\n    font-weight: 400;\n    text-align: center;\n    color: #666666;\n    line-height: 17px;\n}\n\n/* 失败状态文字 */\n.login-modal-fail-title {\n    font-size: 14px;\n    font-weight: 400;\n    text-align: center;\n    color: #181818;\n    line-height: 17px;\n    margin-bottom: 2px;\n}\n\n.login-modal-fail-msg {\n    font-size: 12px;\n    font-weight: 400;\n    text-align: center;\n    color: #666666;\n    line-height: 17px;\n    margin-bottom: 4px;\n}\n\n.login-modal-return-btn {\n    font-size: 14px;\n    font-weight: 400;\n    text-align: center;\n    color: #499bf4;\n    line-height: 17px;\n    cursor: pointer;\n}\n\n/**\n * 加载中提示\n */\n.login-modal-loading {\n    display: flex;\n    justify-content: center;\n    align-items: center;\n    width: 100%;\n    height: 100%;\n}\n\n.login-modal-loading::after {\n    content: '加载中...';\n    font-size: 12px;\n    color: #666;\n}\n</style>\n\n<!-- 弹窗DOM结构 -->\n<div class=\"login-modal-overlay\" id=\"loginModalOverlay\">\n    <div class=\"login-modal\" id=\"loginModal\">\n        <!-- 关闭按钮 -->\n        <div class=\"login-modal-close\" id=\"loginModalClose\"></div>\n        \n        <!-- 标题 -->\n        <div class=\"login-modal-title\" id=\"loginModalTitle\">中国体育彩票APP扫码登录</div>\n        \n        <!-- 二维码区域 -->\n        <div class=\"login-modal-qr-container\" id=\"loginModalQrContainer\">\n            <!-- 二维码主体 -->\n            <div class=\"login-modal-qr-box\" id=\"loginModalQrBox\">\n                <div class=\"login-modal-qr-code\" id=\"loginModalQrCode\"></div>\n                <!-- 遮罩层 - 未勾选协议时显示 -->\n                <div class=\"login-modal-mask\" id=\"loginModalMask\">\n                    <div class=\"login-modal-mask-text\">请先阅读<br>并勾选下方协议</div>\n                </div>\n                <!-- 状态结果区域 - 成功/过期/失败时显示 -->\n                <div class=\"login-modal-result\" id=\"loginModalResult\">\n                    <div class=\"login-modal-result-img\" id=\"loginModalResultImg\"></div>\n                    <div class=\"login-modal-result-text\" id=\"loginModalResultText\"></div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        \n        <!-- APP下载浮层 - 鼠标悬停时显示(仅APP模式) -->\n        <div class=\"login-modal-app-download app-mode\" id=\"loginModalAppDownload\">\n            <img src=\"https://static.sporttery.cn/res_1_0/jcw/images/login/appOver.png\" alt=\"扫码下载APP\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: contain;\">\n        </div>\n        \n        <!-- 描述文字 -->\n        <div class=\"login-modal-desc\" id=\"loginModalDesc\">\n            使用微信/支付宝扫码后在中国体育彩票<br>小程序完成授权登录\n        </div>\n        \n        <!-- 用户协议勾选 -->\n        <div class=\"login-modal-agreement\">\n            <label style=\"cursor: pointer; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;\">\n                <input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"loginModalAgreement\" class=\"login-modal-checkbox\">\n                我已阅读并同意<a href=\"https://www.sporttery.cn/bzzx/20260410/10053082.html?gid=91\" target=\"_blank\">《用户协议》</a>及<a href=\"https://www.sporttery.cn/bzzx/20260410/10053080.html?gid=91\" target=\"_blank\">《隐私政策》</a>\n            </label>\n        </div>\n        \n        <!-- APP模式提示文字 -->\n        <div class=\"login-modal-app-notice\" id=\"loginModalAppNotice\">安卓、iOS系统用户请使用体彩APP 3.10.0及以上版本<br>鸿蒙系统用户请使用体彩APP 3.7.4及以上版本</div>\n        \n        <!-- 登录状态提示 -->\n        <div class=\"login-modal-status\" id=\"loginModalStatus\"></div>\n        \n        <!-- 倒计时 -->\n        <div class=\"login-modal-countdown\" id=\"loginModalCountdown\"></div>\n        \n        <!-- 切换按钮 -->\n        <div class=\"login-modal-switch\" id=\"loginModalSwitch\">\n            <div class=\"login-modal-switch-content\">\n                <div class=\"login-modal-switch-text\"><span id=\"loginModalSwitchText\">微信/支付宝扫码登录</span><span class=\"login-modal-switch-arrow\"></span></div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n`;var LoginModal={getGenerateQrCode:_PCw$.bL,currentQrType:_PCw$.n(_PCw$.t),isAgreementChecked:_PCw$.bL,qrExpireTime:_PCw$.u,qrTimer:null,checkTimer:null,currentQrId:null,qrCode:_PCw$.q(_PCw$.s),isScannedDisplayed:_PCw$.bL,currentStatus:_PCw$.o(_PCw$.v),merchantCode:_PCw$.o(_PCw$.w),sceneCode:_PCw$.o(_PCw$.x),redirectUri:_PCw$.p(_PCw$.t),show:function(){var overlay=document.getElementById(_PCw$.o(_PCw$.y));var _0xb=_PCw$.s,_S$Sf=_PCw$.z;while(_PCw$.bM){switch(_PCw$.b[_0xb++]^_S$Sf){case[_S$Sf=_PCw$.A,_PCw$.B][_PCw$.t]:if(overlay){overlay.style.display=_PCw$.n(_PCw$.C);this.init()}else{document.body.insert